      <title>南非能源计划将于三月提交给立法者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/south-africa-s-energy-plan-to-be-submitted-to-lawmakers-by-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非电力部长 Kgosientsho Ramokgopa 表示，南非政府预计将于本月完成国家能源蓝图的修订，并在第一季度末向立法者提交拟议的修改方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/south-africa-s-energy-plan-to-be-submitted-to-lawmakers-by-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:22:36 GMT</pubDate>
